  "bodyHtml": "<div class=\"is-container-in\">\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column full\">\n<h1 class=\"size-64 is-title1-64 is-title-bold\">AI進展超乎意料地快!</h1>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column full\">\n<p class=\"normal-txt\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">~宗翰老師文~<br />\n<br />\nDeepMind的AlphaProof/Geometry2 已經可拿下今年IMO銀牌 而且解出兩題最難壓軸題！<br />\n不敢想像 十年後 多少的白領工作將被替代或壓縮!!<br />\nAI未來將無法通過圖靈測試，因為太容易被辨認出來，它比人類厲害太多!!<br />\n（Turing test是要求電腦能成功偽裝人類）<br />\n---<br />\n來源：Google DeepMind<br />\nBreakthrough models AlphaProof and AlphaGeometry 2 solve advanced reasoning problems in mathematics<br />\n---<br />\n詳情請見下方臉連結:<br />\n<a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/permalink/1535172790768734/\" title=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3498db;\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/permalink/1535172790768734/</span></a></span></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column full\">\n<div class=\"center has-btn-edit two\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"btn-html btn-primary edit\" href=\"https://deepmind.google/discover/blog/ai-solves-imo-problems-at-silver-medal-level/?fbclid=IwY2xjawEV1ehleHRuA2FlbQIxMQABHaav4Vz86g27-9a0vH_yF7Em1354TB-g0yapK8twHaJjocY0C8dcmBeEhg_aem_aCmN6v2HKLIQt3_oOzLMpw\">Google DeepMind</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>",
